                     <interp inst="t17991030-58-off333" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17991030-58-off333" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17991030-58-cd334" type="crimeDate">22d of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991030-58-off333 t17991030-58-cd334"></join>, a brown-mare, value 6l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17991030-58-victim588" type="victimName">
                     Joseph 
                     Hills
                  <interp inst="t17991030-58-victim588" type="surname" value="Hills"></interp>
