                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991030-58-defend586 t17991030-58-punish338"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 23.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
